{"Id":483,"LanguageCodes":["zh","zho"],"Name":"zho-majian1","Author":"Ma Jian","Language":"Chinese(traditional)","Description":"Chinese(traditional)","Direction":"ltr","Source":"http://tanzil.net","Translations":[{"SurahNumber":53,"VerseNumber":45,"Text":"他曾創造配偶──男性的與女性的──"},{"SurahNumber":53,"VerseNumber":46,"Text":"是以射出的精液；"},{"SurahNumber":53,"VerseNumber":47,"Text":"他以再造為自己的責任；"},{"SurahNumber":53,"VerseNumber":48,"Text":"他能使人富足，能使人滿意；"},{"SurahNumber":53,"VerseNumber":49,"Text":"他是天狼星的主。"},{"SurahNumber":53,"VerseNumber":50,"Text":"他毀滅了古時的阿德人，"},{"SurahNumber":53,"VerseNumber":51,"Text":"和賽莫德人，而未曾有所遺留；"},{"SurahNumber":53,"VerseNumber":52,"Text":"以前，他毀滅了努哈的宗族。他們確是更不義的，確是更放蕩的。"},{"SurahNumber":53,"VerseNumber":53,"Text":"他使那被顛覆的城市覆亡，"},{"SurahNumber":53,"VerseNumber":54,"Text":"故覆蓋的東西曾覆蓋了那城市。"},{"SurahNumber":53,"VerseNumber":55,"Text":"你懷疑你的主的哪一件恩典呢？"},{"SurahNumber":53,"VerseNumber":56,"Text":"這是古時的那些警告者之中的一個警告者。"},{"SurahNumber":53,"VerseNumber":57,"Text":"臨近的事件，已經臨近了；"},{"SurahNumber":53,"VerseNumber":58,"Text":"除真主外，沒有能揭示它的。"},{"SurahNumber":53,"VerseNumber":59,"Text":"難道你們為這訓辭而詫異嗎？"},{"SurahNumber":53,"VerseNumber":60,"Text":"你們怎麼嘲笑而不痛哭呢？"},{"SurahNumber":53,"VerseNumber":61,"Text":"你們是疏忽的。"},{"SurahNumber":53,"VerseNumber":62,"Text":"你們應當為真主而叩頭，應當崇拜他。"},{"SurahNumber":54,"VerseNumber":1,"Text":"復活時臨近了，月亮破裂了。"},{"SurahNumber":54,"VerseNumber":2,"Text":"如果他們看見一種蹟象，他們就退避，而且說：「這是一種有力的魔術。」"},{"SurahNumber":54,"VerseNumber":3,"Text":"他們否認他，而且順從私欲。每一件事都是確定的。"},{"SurahNumber":54,"VerseNumber":4,"Text":"包含警戒的許多消息，確已來臨他們了，"},{"SurahNumber":54,"VerseNumber":5,"Text":"那是極精密的智慧；但警告是無效的，"},{"SurahNumber":54,"VerseNumber":6,"Text":"故你應當避開他們。當召喚者召人於難事的日子，"}]}